<i>noun</i>: 첨삭 [첨삭], 정정 [정정], 시정 [시ː정], 수정 [수정], 수술 [수술], 보정 [보ː정], 교정 [교ː정], 가필 [가필] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>첨삭 [첨삭]</dt><br>
<dd>correction; editing</dd><br>
<dd>남이 쓴 글이나 답안 등에 내용을 일부 보태거나 삭제하여 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of revising another person's writing, answers, etc., by adding, deleting, or correcting.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정정 [정정]</dt><br>
<dd>correction</dd><br>
<dd>글자, 글, 말 등의 잘못된 곳을 고쳐서 바로잡음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of changing and making right what is wrong in a letter, text, speech, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>시정 [시ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>rectification; correction</dd><br>
<dd>잘못된 것을 바르게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of correcting a wrong thing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수정 [수정]</dt><br>
<dd>correction; rectification</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 글자의 잘못된 부분을 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of correcting the wrong parts of a piece of writing or a letter.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수술 [수술]</dt><br>
<dd>1. surgery; operation</dd><br>
<dd>병을 고치기 위하여 몸의 한 부분을 째고 자르거나 붙이고 꿰매는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of slitting, cutting, attaching, and stitching a body part or organ in order to treat an illness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. correction</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 결함을 근본적으로 고치는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An act of fixing a flaw in a fundamental manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>보정 [보ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>correction; revision</dd><br>
<dd>부족한 부분을 보태거나 고쳐서 바르게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making up for shortcomings of something or revising it to make it correct.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>교정 [교ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. correction</dd><br>
<dd>고르지 못하거나 틀어지거나 잘못된 것을 바로잡음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of correcting something uneven, distorted or wrong.</dd><br>
<dd>2. correction; remediation</dd><br>
<dd>교도소나 소년원 등에서 죄를 지은 사람의 품성과 행동을 바로잡음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of correcting the personality or behavior of persons who committed crimes and have been detained in prison or juvenile hall.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가필 [가필]</dt><br>
<dd>1. correction; revision</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 문서를 부분적으로 고쳐 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of rewriting a statement or document partially.</dd><br>
<dd>2. retouching</dd><br>
<dd>글씨나 그림의 부분을 지우거나 덧칠하여 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of changing a letter or painting by partially erasing or painting over it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>